msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Salary Sacrificed Workplace Giving`\\ 額を設定します（例：控除の代"
"わりに福利厚生を受け取る）。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:160
msgid ":guilabel:`Super contributions`"
