msgstr ""
"**CNC意見書S100**：`貸借対照表に関する質問と回答 <https://www.nbb.be/doc/ba/"
"models/social%20balance/avis_cnc_s100.pdf>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:2431
